text: Jovana Jakšić and Renata Zarazúa were the defending champions, but both players chose not to participate. Sanaz Marand and Caitlin Whoriskey won the title, defeating wildcards Vladica Babić and Julia Rosenqvist in the final, 7–6(7–4), 6–4. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== *Main Draw Braidy Industries Women's Tennis Classic - Doubles
